---
// タスク整理表 — ユーザータスク → システムタスク / CRUD分類の図解
---

<figure class="tt-diagram" aria-label="タスク整理表の構造を示す図">
  <div class="tt-diagram__inner">
    <span class="tt-diagram__title-label">タスク整理表の構造</span>

    <div class="tt-diagram__table-wrap">
      <table class="tt-diagram__table">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th class="tt-diagram__th tt-diagram__th--user">ユーザーのタスク</th
            >
            <th class="tt-diagram__th tt-diagram__th--system"
              >システム側のタスク</th
            >
            <th class="tt-diagram__th tt-diagram__th--crud">CRUD</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td class="tt-diagram__td">購入履歴を確認する</td>
            <td class="tt-diagram__td">購入データを取得し一覧表示する</td>
            <td class="tt-diagram__td"
              ><span class="tt-diagram__crud tt-diagram__crud--r">R</span></td
            >
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="tt-diagram__td">配送先を登録する</td>
            <td class="tt-diagram__td">住所データを新規作成・保存する</td>
            <td class="tt-diagram__td"
              ><span class="tt-diagram__crud tt-diagram__crud--c">C</span></td
            >
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="tt-diagram__td">配送先を変更する</td>
            <td class="tt-diagram__td">住所データを更新する</td>
            <td class="tt-diagram__td"
              ><span class="tt-diagram__crud tt-diagram__crud--u">U</span></td
            >
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="tt-diagram__td">カートを空にする</td>
            <td class="tt-diagram__td">選択中の商品データを削除する</td>
            <td class="tt-diagram__td"
              ><span class="tt-diagram__crud tt-diagram__crud--d">D</span></td
            >
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <!-- CRUD legend -->
    <div class="tt-diagram__legend">
      <span class="tt-diagram__legend-label">CRUD</span>
      <ul class="tt-diagram__legend-list">
        <li>
          <span class="tt-diagram__crud tt-diagram__crud--c">C</span> Create — 作成
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="tt-diagram__crud tt-diagram__crud--r">R</span> Read — 参照
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="tt-diagram__crud tt-diagram__crud--u">U</span> Update — 更新
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="tt-diagram__crud tt-diagram__crud--d">D</span> Delete — 削除
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
  <figcaption class="tt-diagram__caption">
    ユーザー視点の動詞をCRUDで分類することで、機能の抜け漏れと粒度のばらつきを防ぐ。
  </figcaption>
</figure>

<style>
  .tt-diagram {
    margin-block: 2.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 6px;
    background: linear-gradient(
      160deg,
      color-mix(in oklch, var(--surface) 80%, white),
      var(--surface)
    );
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .tt-diagram__inner {
    padding: 1.75rem 1.5rem 1.25rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.1rem;
  }

  .tt-diagram__title-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.67rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-faint);
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* Table */
  .tt-diagram__table-wrap {
    overflow-x: auto;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  .tt-diagram__table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    background: var(--bg);
  }

  .tt-diagram__th {
    padding: 0.55rem 0.85rem;
    font-size: 0.67rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-align: left;
    border-block-end: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .tt-diagram__th--user {
    color: var(--accent-deep);
    background: color-mix(in oklch, var(--accent-wash) 60%, var(--bg));
  }

  .tt-diagram__th--system {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    background: color-mix(in oklch, var(--surface) 80%, var(--bg));
  }

  .tt-diagram__th--crud {
    color: var(--text-faint);
    background: color-mix(in oklch, var(--surface) 80%, var(--bg));
    text-align: center;
    width: 4rem;
  }

  .tt-diagram__td {
    padding: 0.55rem 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.55;
    border-block-end: 1px solid var(--border);
    vertical-align: middle;

    &:last-child {
      text-align: center;
    }
  }

  tr:last-child .tt-diagram__td {
    border-block-end: none;
  }

  tr:nth-child(even) .tt-diagram__td {
    background: color-mix(in oklch, var(--surface) 40%, transparent);
  }

  /* CRUD badges */
  .tt-diagram__crud {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    padding: 0.15rem 0.45rem;
    border-radius: 3px;
    line-height: 1.4;
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
  }

  .tt-diagram__crud--c {
    color: color-mix(in oklch, var(--accent-deep) 90%, oklch(0.4 0.15 145));
    background: color-mix(in oklch, oklch(0.88 0.08 145) 30%, var(--bg));
    border: 1px solid color-mix(in oklch, oklch(0.7 0.1 145) 30%, transparent);
  }

  .tt-diagram__crud--r {
    color: var(--accent-deep);
    background: color-mix(in oklch, var(--accent-wash) 80%, transparent);
    border: 1px solid color-mix(in oklch, var(--accent) 30%, transparent);
  }

  .tt-diagram__crud--u {
    color: color-mix(in oklch, var(--text-muted) 90%, oklch(0.45 0.12 240));
    background: color-mix(in oklch, oklch(0.87 0.06 240) 30%, var(--bg));
    border: 1px solid color-mix(in oklch, oklch(0.6 0.1 240) 25%, transparent);
  }

  .tt-diagram__crud--d {
    color: var(--text-faint);
    background: color-mix(in oklch, var(--surface) 80%, transparent);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  /* Legend */
  .tt-diagram__legend {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .tt-diagram__legend-label {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-faint);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .tt-diagram__legend-list {
    list-style: none !important;
    padding: 0 !important;
    margin: 0 !important;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.3rem 1rem;

    & li {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.4rem;
      font-size: 0.74rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      margin: 0 !important;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }
  }

  /* Caption */
  .tt-diagram__caption {
    padding: 0.55rem 1.5rem 0.6rem;
    font-size: 0.74rem;
    color: var(--text-faint);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    border-block-start: 1px solid var(--border);
    text-align: center;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  @media (max-width: 520px) {
    .tt-diagram__inner {
      padding: 1.25rem 1rem 1rem;
    }

    .tt-diagram__td,
    .tt-diagram__th {
      padding: 0.5rem 0.65rem;
    }
  }
</style>
